{"tid":960260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英預言家：明年中國經濟衰退 債務泡沫破裂","createTime":"2018-12-29T09:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T05:52:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5c01e1337a024c8569c67a03f96dccc92c1204e8","tid":960260,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:17:00.000Z","msg":"英預言家：明年中國經濟衰退 債務泡沫破裂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/12/28/n10937862.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F12%2F28%2Fn10937862.htm&d=K8PvC2QKr1Z73RSyGz68H7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cb6ba896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/12/28/n10937862.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2018年12月28日訊】（大紀元記者陳俊村編譯報導）英國南安普敦（Southampton）男子漢密爾頓-帕克（Craig Hamilton-Parker）自稱預言家，先前曾成功預言川普（特朗普）當選美國總統。他最近針對2019年的國際局勢預言說，中國經濟會出現衰退，導致債務泡沫破裂，民眾因而走上街頭抗議。<br />\n<br />\n漢密爾頓-帕克每年都會預言來年的重大事件，並在YouTube網站和其個人網站上發表。有別於其他預言家，他會驗證先前預言的準確性，甚至給自己評分。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以2018年來說，他先前預言美國會在墨西哥邊境啟用無人機和感測器，而不會修建圍牆。但事實上，川普計劃興建圍牆，而且正在籌措經費，所以他承認這項預言錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他預言美國加州和澳洲會發生野火，而印度則會發生洪水，結果真的發生了。他認為他的預言準確，給自己評分為10/10。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n針對即將到來的2019年，漢密爾頓-帕克在今年9月做出一系列預言，以下列舉其中比較重大的事件供讀者參考：<br />\n<br />\n●俄羅斯駭客入侵英國銀行系統。<br />\n<br />\n●美國與俄羅斯因敘利亞問題而產生的衝突升溫。美國在以色列部署兵力。<br />\n<br />\n●川普生病，但無生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n●外界持續推動對川普的彈劾，但以失敗告終。他會連任總統。<br />\n<br />\n●川普與巴基斯坦達成一項貿易協議，以換取該國驅逐恐怖分子和極端主義者。這些人會被趕到阿富汗。<br />\n<br />\n●美國國家航空航天局（NASA）宣布在月球興建基地以取得稀土的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n●美國國家航空航天局（NASA）宣布在月球歐洲議會選舉，右翼勝出。<br />\n<br />\n●中國步入經濟蕭條，債務泡沫破裂，民眾走上街頭（抗議）。<br />\n<br />\n●俄羅斯被大型隕石擊中。<br />\n<br />\n●尼泊爾發生破壞性極大的地震。<br />\n<br />\n●雖然朝鮮與美國達成協議，但該國領導人金正恩最終還是被其人民推翻。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n（編者按：漢密爾頓-帕克在2018年預言中也提到金正恩會被人民推翻，但目前尚未發生。）</span></span>"},{"pid":"02ef7ac86dd36d1815c6d3d60b799dac5d6ea8a5","tid":960260,"uid":18569,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"年年都話支爆支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648015f558abffb594251970f28cb9dc988a11ed","tid":960260,"uid":191352,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e36691250c327704ac52ffb42cc34855e221bf43","tid":960260,"uid":183520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"大紀元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0749930c7669a228664219b806d9d061bfa64fef","tid":960260,"uid":54754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"睇侵侵點撚狗仲好"},{"pid":"aa879e768dcf66f1d353422dcbd8b9fe876efba2","tid":960260,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"第二個預言侵侵會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8322e6d6f4e75555c679733c5246d4b56330eb3e","tid":960260,"uid":550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aa879e768dcf66f1d353422dcbd8b9fe876efba2","tid":960260,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"第二個預言侵侵會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"傷風感冒打乞痴都可以話老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827d874ab2123b6077959e363606056eb34fbd21","tid":960260,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8322e6d6f4e75555c679733c5246d4b56330eb3e","tid":960260,"uid":550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aa879e768dcf66f1d353422dcbd8b9fe876efba2","tid":960260,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"第二個預言侵侵會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:41:46.000Z","msg":"傷風感冒打乞痴都可以話老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"另一個話佢中聲波攻擊會失聰"},{"pid":"c24207ea2b77649fb789b3667a7d460f1376df51","tid":960260,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家又一堆馬後炮衝哂出黎"},{"pid":"4d969399684284736895a3333a4f7b09ef7e55d9","tid":960260,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"不如買定花生<br />\n睇盲毛係咪批中 大海嘯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b7a20299bf8bfe6cbf352ab13f3a65579dc799","tid":960260,"uid":35870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"中國步入經濟蕭條，債務泡沫破裂，<span style=\"color: red;\">民眾走上街頭（抗議）。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nd鬼佬真係唔識架喎.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走上街頭抗議？睇黎佢對国情唔太理解"},{"pid":"95e1ca48eaf1cbc36b1491ce9acfbd469edf68ff","tid":960260,"uid":55897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"應該依家就爆緊,但就收得好密,好多人都失業,離開城市返鄕下."},{"pid":"858ec8bd04d73f9f263b73138225e0c79c062bd0","tid":960260,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95e1ca48eaf1cbc36b1491ce9acfbd469edf68ff","tid":960260,"uid":55897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"應該依家就爆緊,但就收得好密,好多人都失業,離開城市返鄕下."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"一定走上街，行乞咁解唶！<br />\n以千萬計失業軍<br />\n屌！根本得打仗一條路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0b11b83091ad500197daf2c02e35f6396b69ee","tid":960260,"uid":169484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c01e1337a024c8569c67a03f96dccc92c1204e8","tid":960260,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T09:17: